WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: yKot6Plxn7Y

NOTE Language: en

00:00:06.314 --> 00:00:12.604
I was very lucky that I was able to meet
with Shri Mataji when I was about

00:00:12.604 --> 00:00:18.912
18 years old and She was staying in Bombay
and She was, at that time, the wife of

00:00:18.912 --> 00:00:23.974
The Chairman of The Shipping Corporation
of India. My mother knew Her, so we went

00:00:23.974 --> 00:00:29.873
over to Her home and my mother said, "Here
is a special person and you'll feel good

00:00:29.873 --> 00:00:34.824
if you meet Her." There were not that many
people. There were a few people in Bombay,

00:00:34.824 --> 00:00:39.885
they'd meet for meditation. In fact, when
they met for meditation, Shri Mataji

00:00:39.885 --> 00:00:46.060
Herself would be there, sitting in front
of everybody but it took a few years after

00:00:46.060 --> 00:00:50.541
that to fully realize the power
of the vibrations.
